{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"35e1cc82-7947-419d-8232-d1c49d06eb0d","content":"","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_AA90WKn1tt2UxzqN1HHRxs","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Providing crash dump config"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"tooluse_FN2vXPlEZj0hzg0Z0Qbffu","name":"bash","arguments":{"command":"echo \"Providing NativeAOT crash dump configuration for Kubernetes\"","description":"Context check","initial_wait":5},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"Context check"}],"interactionId":"3f59e5eb-f36d-4663-8f22-ac63a604e057","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user wants to configure automatic crash dump collection for a NativeAOT .NET 11 app running in Kubernetes. They have `createdump` installed at `/opt/tools/createdump`. I need to provide:\n\n1. The environment variables needed to configure .NET to use createdump for automatic crash dump collection\n2. The Kubernetes pod spec changes needed\n\nFor NativeAOT .NET apps, crash dump collection works differently than regular CoreCLR apps. In NativeAOT, you typically need to configure the environment to handle crashes and generate dumps.\n\nKey environment variables for .NET crash dumps:\n\n\n- `DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump=1` enables mini dump collection when the app crashes\n- `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType` controls the dump size (1=Mini, 2=Heap, 3=Triage, 4=Full)\n- `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName` specifies the output path and filename pattern for dumps\n- `DOTNET_CreateDumpDiagnostics=1` enables diagnostic output from the createdump tool itself\n\nFor NativeAOT specifically, I need to verify the exact configuration since it doesn't use the standard CoreCLR runtime.\n\nIn .NET 8+, the createdump tool location is specified via `DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath`, so they'd set it to `/opt/tools/createdump`. Beyond the environment variables, Kubernetes needs a volume for storing the dumps, the `SYS_PTRACE` capability so createdump can attach to processes, and these variables configured in the container spec.","outputTokens":604,"requestId":"502D:2C454F:24E24E:2E8A00:69F55487"},"id":"39a2cb92-c608-4298-bb73-c5ff75cc92aa","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:34:12.414Z","parentId":"dcd89d72-d7ef-4562-be38-a4e5082d40a3"}
